  <brief_title>Age-Dependent Impact of the SYNTAX-score on Mortality</brief_title>
  <official_title>Age-Dependent Impact of the SYNTAX-score on Mortality After Percutaneous Coronary Intervention in an All-Comer Population</official_title>
